>>__ Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="hol"};
## `strcat`

``` hol4
Lib.strcat : string -> string -> string
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Concatenates two ML strings.

### Failure

Never fails.

### Example

``` hol4
>> strcat "1" "";

>> strcat "hello" "world";

>> strcat "hello" (strcat " " "world");
```
